# SSC - Stingray Services Controller
# Set of python scripts to query ssc, stingray services controller, used for FLA
#
# SET SSC ADMIN password, in file called ~/.sscrc
# add sscadmin user password, with colon as delimeter.
# i.e.
# echo "sscadmin:<sscadminpassword>" >> ~/.sscrc
#
# or it will prompt for sscadmin password everytime you run the script.

# some example of querying current stm instances
#
# python instance_resource.py -s
# python instance_resource.py -q /api/tmcm/1.0/instance/<instance_name>
# 
####

